            "size": 1600,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_018kLUomEm4RhHw2737toccj\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears.\\n\\nHow do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"automatic calendar scheduling software\\\",\\n    \\\"timezone meeting coordinator\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar sync for global teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting time finder for remote work\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional**: \\\"meeting scheduling tool for remote teams\\\", \\\"automatic calendar scheduling software\\\", \\\"team scheduling across time zones\\\"\\n- **Problem-focused**: \\\"eliminate meeting coordination emails\\\", \\\"timezone meeting coordinator\\\"\\n- **Awareness & comparison**: \\\"best scheduling tool for distributed teams\\\", \\\"calendar sync for global teams\\\"\\n- **Broad intent**: \\\"meeting time finder for remote work\\\"\\n\\nEach keyword reflects the pain point your target audience (remote teams and project managers) is actively searching for. Ready to move forward with these, or would you like me to adjust any?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1142,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":247,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
